&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://blog.lostinmyterminal.com/webpages/2015/01/09/math-support-in-jekyll.html&quot;&gt;1. http://blog.lostinmyterminal.com/webpages/2015/01/09/math-support-in-jekyll.html&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://stackoverflow.com/questions/26275645/how-to-support-latex-in-github-pages&quot;&gt;2. https://stackoverflow.com/questions/26275645/how-to-support-latex-in-github-pages&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
